title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: A spotlight this week on the Federal Reserve's Jackson Hole Symposium, as traders look for clues on the pace of rate hikes. Could chipmaker Nvidia (NVDA) exceed earnings expectations? They are due to report this week, with investors skittish. An upcoming report on dollar stores could tip us off to just how much consumers are pinching pennies.
